Package: lite-nas
Version: @PACKAGE_VERSION@
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: @PACKAGE_ARCH@
Maintainer: Oleksiy Bondar <bondaroleksiyandroyovich@gmail.com>
Pre-Depends: debconf (>= 1.5.0)
Depends: zfsutils-linux, nats-server, nginx, openssl, systemd, ufw
Recommends: aide, clamav, usbguard
Description: LiteNAS bootstrap and host profile package
 Applies the LiteNAS host profile, deploys managed configuration,
 provisions common LiteNAS identities, installs bundled LiteNAS
 service and app binaries, and configures the LiteNAS web gateway
 reverse-proxy and firewall baseline.
